    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed status consistent with MRL 2 requirements. Bench validation demonstrates RH < 1 at all five operating points with maximum prediction error below 5%. The governing Requirement specifies that hemolytic performance shall exhibit minimal adverse impact and results shall be consistent with reasonable engineering expectations; the assessment team judged that the CFD results satisfy these criteria based on the observed RH range and convergence metrics. The package is accepted as providing sufficient credibility evidence for the COU decision.",
